{{flavour|A valuable potion which grants a person with an infusion of magical energy.}}

Quaffing a '''potion of magic''' restores 10-37 [[magic points]], <code>9 + 3d28/3</code><ref>{{source ref|0.30.1|defines.h|165}}</ref>, strongly biased towards the middle values. This potion is quite rare and immensely useful for [[spellcaster]]s.

All Mage backgrounds ([[Hedge Wizard]]s, [[Conjurer]]s, etc.) start with a potion of magic in their inventories.

==History==
*In [[0.18]] alone, [[Pakellas]] gifted potions of magic to its followers.
*Prior to [[0.5]], the potion restored all magic points and had one in three chance of increasing max MP by one.

